Hannah is a surf champion who won the English Nationals and Women's titles of the UK Pro Surf Tour in 2012.

Despite being pregnant she entered Boardmasters last year - and reached the finals.

She has been an ambassador for the Wave Project since 2013, and regularly attends surf club sessions to provide coaching for young people.

